                                </origPlace>, <origDate notAfter="1475" notBefore="1425">15th century, middle of</origDate>. All watermarks seem to point to southern Germany or <placeName ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/place/100208">Austria</placeName> and the middle of the 15th century. The inclusion of a bull by Nicholas V (1397–1455) gives a terminus post quem for that particular text (which appears to be a later addition).</p>
