                            <handDesc>
                                <p>Many different scribes have contributed to the texts, especially to the first text, Summa theologiae. Here, six different hands seem to be involved.</p>
                                <handNote xml:id="hand-1">
                                    <locus from="1r" to="12v" scheme="folios"/>Semihybrida. </handNote>
                                <handNote xml:id="hand-2">
                                    <locus from="13r" to="97v" scheme="folios"/>Cursive or possibly semi-hybrida, some irregular looping. </handNote>
                                <handNote xml:id="hand-3">
                                    <locus from="97v" to="119r" scheme="folios"/>Semihybrida. </handNote>
                                <handNote xml:id="hand-4">
